{
  "1727910": {
    "name": "Hope Trigger",
    "steam_appid": 1727910,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727910/extras/b992cfd438cd33493380806fcd566374.poster.avif?t=1764912825\" width=800 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727910/extras/b992cfd438cd33493380806fcd566374.webm?t=1764912825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727910/extras/b992cfd438cd33493380806fcd566374.mp4?t=1764912825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>『这是一个美丽的国度，生活在这的每个人民，脸上都挂着笑容。这是一个科技的国度，在这里盛行炼金魔法，也是这世界的标竿。但一切都消失，在那蛮族违背誓约的夜晚，失去子民，失去国家。而我被囚禁在那黑暗里。 』</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事始于千年前，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那是一个繁盛文明在一夜之间消逝的时刻，只留下荒芜的废墟与无尽的沉寂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如今，一千年过去，一名少女来到了这片遗迹，并遇见了一位自称是那座亡国女王的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两人携手，踏上揭开失落世界秘密的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而这一切……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只存在于一个无法分辨真假的虚幻世界之中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>========================================================</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HOPE-TRIGGER</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是一款精心打造的 2D 横向动作 RPG，以节奏驱动的成长系统贯穿整体冒险体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将在战斗中切换原罪战斗风格、装备「誓约」，并习得各式强力魔法技能，打破敌阵、找回希望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每当战败时，独特的系统「命运之书的启示」可能觉醒——触发一段动画式重生演出，并依据你的旅程进展，赋予强化效果与新的觉悟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>========================================================</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏系统 :</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A.战斗特色：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727910/extras/b3edbf40cd5bc4eda31c7d2d701903cb.poster.avif?t=1764912825\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727910/extras/b3edbf40cd5bc4eda31c7d2d701903cb.webm?t=1764912825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727910/extras/b3edbf40cd5bc4eda31c7d2d701903cb.mp4?t=1764912825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>原罪连段：玩家可从不同原罪中挑选并切换两种风格，每种皆为独特的三段连击，再搭配固定技能与属性原罪，打造专属的战斗节奏与流派。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样魔法：运用多属性魔法灵活应对危机，释放强大力量，逆转战局。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>招架与反击：掌握精准的招架技巧，破除敌人攻势，并以致命一击反击，扭转战斗局面。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>誓约增益：透过装备复数的誓约，启动各式强化效果，助你在冒险中披荆斩棘，克服各种挑战。 </strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>B.职业系统：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727910/extras/70b402a7308cf761012bda6db0c4315d.poster.avif?t=1764912825\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727910/extras/70b402a7308cf761012bda6db0c4315d.webm?t=1764912825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727910/extras/70b402a7308cf761012bda6db0c4315d.mp4?t=1764912825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>随着故事进行、探索地图或完成任务，逐步解锁各具特色的职业，为冒险增添更多惊喜与挑战。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>透过「爆发」，每个职业都能启动专属强化，全面提升其战斗风格的特性，帮助玩家在关键时刻对抗更强大的敌人。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>四种基础职业（战士、牧师、法师、弓手）可升级为中级 → 高级职业，能力继承并拓展。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>例：牧师 → 武僧：保有恢复量强化的能力，同时强化格斗类型招式。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>进阶职业（巫女、暗杀者、魔剑士…等）需透过任务解锁，并可能改变操作方式（例如将「射箭」改为「刺杀」），带来全新的战斗手感。</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >C.冒险特色：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727910/extras/6ac74ffda4473e54ff08ac64be0abe0a.poster.avif?t=1764912825\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727910/extras/6ac74ffda4473e54ff08ac64be0abe0a.webm?t=1764912825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727910/extras/6ac74ffda4473e54ff08ac64be0abe0a.mp4?t=1764912825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索：穿梭于充满谜题与惊喜的迷宫地图，发掘隐藏的宝藏，体验无穷的探索乐趣。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采集与制作：搜集多样素材，亲手制作强力装备与美味料理，为冒险增添更多可能性。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任务：与这片世界中形形色色的人物相遇，帮助他们解决困境，倾听他们动人的故事，共同编织冒险的篇章。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >D.养成特色：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727910/extras/36e8a0d527524adc4744542981d9b4e7.poster.avif?t=1764912825\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727910/extras/36e8a0d527524adc4744542981d9b4e7.webm?t=1764912825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727910/extras/36e8a0d527524adc4744542981d9b4e7.mp4?t=1764912825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原核节点：透过任务、制作或讨伐获得的特殊装备，可改变原罪战斗型态、提升基础数值（暴击、攻击、防御），或强化职业特性。玩家需在有限格数内取舍，打造专属 Build。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >炼金术：运用素材链成多样原核节点，解锁全新战斗风格，让每场战斗更具策略性与个性化。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阿尔克纳：探索迷宫并收集特殊道具，启动阿尔克纳被动技能，全面提升角色能力，为冒险增添更多可能性。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >E.方舟:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727910/extras/84afca4c6dedb0effc31b6646d63b04b.poster.avif?t=1764912825\" width=256 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727910/extras/84afca4c6dedb0effc31b6646d63b04b.webm?t=1764912825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727910/extras/84afca4c6dedb0effc31b6646d63b04b.mp4?t=1764912825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >实验体的使命：身为实验生命体，你将穿越记忆的世界，揭开谜团，寻找拯救即将崩坏世界的方法。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >记忆承受极限：实验体极其脆弱，无法承受记忆世界中的多次死亡，请谨慎行动，保护好他。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >备份机制：通过备份功能，实验体的记录可回到指定的备份点，避免意识崩溃，为冒险保留一线生机。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >F. 命运之书的启示</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727910/extras/5141e34a60589dcac05a9a15398b1fa2.poster.avif?t=1764912825\" width=320 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727910/extras/5141e34a60589dcac05a9a15398b1fa2.webm?t=1764912825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1727910/extras/5141e34a60589dcac05a9a15398b1fa2.mp4?t=1764912825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战败并非终点，而是力量觉醒的契机。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次败北，都可能触发「命运之书的启示」，为你带来全新的可能性，改写属于你的未来。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >触发后不仅会强化角色本身能力，还会解锁命运等级；随着命运等级的提升，将开启更高层次的成长之路。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >========================================================</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >双连段系统：可装备两种「原罪战斗风格」，在战斗中自由切换，展开独特的三段连击。针对不同敌人展开爽快对战，体验极致打击快感。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特魔法系统：从怪物身上提取红魔素，转化为魔力，施放华丽而致命的魔法攻击，以压倒性的火力扭转战局。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >职业进阶：四种基础职业（战士、牧师、法师、弓手）皆能进化至更高阶职业，解锁专属爆发强化，塑造多样的战斗流派。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原核节点：透过任务、制作或讨伐获得的特殊装备，可改变原罪战斗型态、提升基础数值（暴击、攻击、防御），或强化职业特性。装备格数有限，玩家必须在取舍中创造专属 Build，形成独特的战斗策略。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >命运之书的启示：败北并非终点，而是力量觉醒的契机。每一次试炼，都可能唤醒命运之力，带来新的能力与挑战，为旅程开启全新的可能性。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >========================================================</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>强烈建议使用手把。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >========================================================</p>",
